    <item>
      <title>特鲁多希望加拿大央行“更快”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/trudeau-hopes-bank-of-canada-rate-cuts-will-come-sooner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，他希望加拿大央行在通胀率降至央行目标范围内后很快开始放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/trudeau-hopes-bank-of-canada-rate-cuts-will-come-sooner</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 19:58:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布托政党加入谢里夫联盟寻求治理巴基斯坦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/bhutto-s-party-joins-sharif-s-coalition-seeking-to-run-pakistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布托·扎尔达里家族控制的巴基斯坦政党将加入谢赫巴兹·谢里夫领导的联盟，结束了候任总理在一系列谈判后的僵局，这些谈判将使他们的主要竞争对手伊姆兰·汗失去权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/bhutto-s-party-joins-sharif-s-coalition-seeking-to-run-pakistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 19:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多为 BC 省住宅建设提供高达 15 亿加元的融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/trudeau-offers-up-to-1-5b-in-financing-for-bc-homebuilding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多周二宣布，加拿大政府将提供高达 20 亿加元（15 亿美元）的低成本融资，以加速不列颠哥伦比亚省中等收入家庭的住房建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/trudeau-offers-up-to-1-5b-in-financing-for-bc-homebuilding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 18:48:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大多数德克萨斯州选民预计选举后会爆发暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/most-texas-voters-think-violence-will-erupt-after-2024-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，大约 60% 的德克萨斯州选民预计 11 月选举后将会出现暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/most-texas-voters-think-violence-will-erupt-after-2024-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 17:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
